redcap:ProjectDashboards.title: How to initialize this project
redcap:ProjectDashboards.body:
1. Enable the Admin Dashboard external module on this project
  2. Ensure the correct project id is set in the Admin Dashboard module configuration here: [redcap-version-url]ExternalModules/manager/control_center.php
    1. Click the "Configure' button on Admin Dashboard
    2. Check that the "Project ID of report configuration project" field value is the correct project id.
  3. Go to the online designer
    1. Go to the "Column Formatting" instrument
    2. Edit link_source_column field
    3. If there's already a query in the sql query box and it matches what's in the field note, skip the next 4 steps
      1. Copy and paste the field note into the sql query box
      2. Remove the 2 BRs and everything before it
      3. Should end up with: select value, value from redcap_data where project_id = project-id and field_name = "column_name" and record = record-name order by instance asc
      4. Ensure "project-id" and "record-name" above are wrapped in brackets [ ] to activate the smart variable.
  4. Go to record 1
    1. Go to the "app_title#group" instance of the column formatting form. (Should be instance 6 or "Project Titles" by default).
    2. Ensure the "Source column for generating URLs" field is generating the choices as expected (and that the correct one is selected).

ItemData.Value: List of all users and the projects to which they have access.

select users.username, -- 'username' users.user_lastname, -- 'user_lastname' users.user_firstname, -- 'user_firstname' users.user_email, -- 'user_email' group_concat( projects.project_id order by app_title asc separator '@@@') as 'project_id#group#hidden', group_concat( projects.app_title order by app_title asc separator '@@@') as 'app_title#group', group_concat( if(projects.completed_time is null, '', projects.completed_time) order by app_title asc separator '@@@') as 'completed_time#group#hidden', group_concat( if(projects.date_deleted is null, '', projects.date_deleted) order by app_title asc separator '@@@') as 'date_deleted#group#hidden', count(projects.project_id) as 'project_id_count', users.user_suspended_time as 'user_suspended_time#hidden', group_concat( projects.status order by app_title asc separator '@@@') as 'status#group#hidden' from redcap_user_information as users left join redcap_user_rights as rights on rights.username = users.username left join redcap_projects as projects on projects.project_id = rights.project_id group by users.username order by users.username asc
List of all projects and the users which have access.

select projects.project_id, -- 'project_id' projects.app_title, -- 'app_title' projects.status, -- 'status' if(record_count is null, 0, record_count) as 'record_count', projects.purpose, -- 'purpose' group_concat( if(users.username is null, rights.username, users.username) order by users.username desc separator '@@@') as 'username#group', projects.creation_time, -- 'creation_time' projects.last_logged_event, -- 'last_logged_event' datediff(now(), projects.last_logged_event) as 'days_since_last_event', count(rights.username) as 'username_count', projects.date_deleted as 'date_deleted#hidden', group_concat( if(users.user_suspended_time is null, '', users.user_suspended_time) order by users.username desc separator '@@@') as 'user_suspended_time#group#hidden' from redcap_projects as projects left join redcap_record_counts as rcounts on rcounts.project_id = projects.project_id left join redcap_user_rights as rights on rights.project_id = projects.project_id left join redcap_user_information as users on users.username = rights.username group by projects.project_id order by projects.project_id desc
List of all projects identified as being used for research purposes.

select projects.project_id, -- 'project_id' projects.app_title, -- 'app_title' projects.status, -- 'status' if(rcounts.record_count is null, 0, rcounts.record_count) as 'record_count', projects.purpose_other, -- 'purpose_other' projects.project_pi_lastname, -- 'project_pi_lastname' projects.project_pi_firstname, -- 'project_pi_firstname' projects.project_pi_email, -- 'project_pi_email' projects.project_irb_number, -- 'project_irb_number' projects.creation_time as 'creation_time', projects.last_logged_event as 'last_logged_event', datediff(now(), projects.last_logged_event) as 'last_logged_event_days' from redcap_projects as projects left join redcap_record_counts as rcounts on rcounts.project_id = projects.project_id where projects.purpose = 2 order by projects.project_id desc
List of all projects currently in Development status.

select projects.project_id, -- 'project_id' projects.app_title, -- 'app_title' IF(record_count is null, 0, record_count) as 'record_count', projects.purpose as 'purpose', projects.creation_time as 'creation_time', projects.last_logged_event as 'last_logged_event', datediff(now(), projects.last_logged_event) as 'last_logged_event_diff', projects.date_deleted as 'date_deleted#hidden' from redcap_projects as projects left join redcap_record_counts as rcounts on rcounts.project_id = projects.project_id where projects.status = 0 order by projects.project_id desc

select projects.project_id, -- 'project_id' projects.app_title, -- 'app_title' if(rcounts.record_count is null, 0, rcounts.record_count) as 'record_count', projects.status, -- 'status' projects.purpose, -- 'purpose' projects.creation_time, -- 'creation_time' projects.last_logged_event as 'last_logged_event', cast(datediff( now(), projects.last_logged_event) as char(50)) as 'last_logged_event_days', projects.date_deleted as 'date_deleted#hidden' from redcap_projects as projects left join redcap_record_counts as rcounts on rcounts.project_id = projects.project_id order by projects.project_id desc
List of External Modules and the projects they are enabled in.

select modules.directory_prefix, -- 'directory_prefix' group_concat( distinct projects.app_title order by projects.app_title asc separator '@@@') as 'app_title#group', group_concat( distinct users.user_email order by users.user_email asc separator '@@@') as 'user_email#group', count( distinct projects.project_id) as 'project_id_count', group_concat( distinct projects.project_id order by projects.app_title asc separator '@@@') as 'project_id#group#hidden', group_concat( distinct projects.status order by app_title asc separator '@@@') as 'status#group#hidden', group_concat( if(projects.date_deleted is null, '', projects.date_deleted) order by projects.app_title asc separator '@@@') as 'date_deleted#group#hidden' from redcap_external_module_settings as settings left join redcap_external_modules as modules on modules.external_module_id = settings.external_module_id left join redcap_projects as projects on projects.project_id = settings.project_id left join redcap_user_rights as rights on rights.project_id = projects.project_id left join redcap_user_information as users on users.username = rights.username where settings.key = 'enabled' and (settings.value = 'true' or settings.value = 'enabled') and settings.project_id is not null group by settings.external_module_id order by directory_prefix
List of projects recently accessed by the currently logged in user.

select distinct projects.project_id, -- 'project_id' projects.app_title, -- 'app_title' max(ts) as "last_access_timestamp", projects.status as "status#hidden" from redcap_log_view as logs left join redcap_projects as projects on logs.project_id = projects.project_id where projects.project_id is not null and logs.event = 'PAGE_VIEW' and logs.user = '[user-name]' group by logs.project_id order by last_access_timestamp desc limit 50
